---
title: Ginger-Glazed Tofu Bowls with Toasted Cashews, Pickled Radishes and Cilantro Rice
description: Hearty tofu is smothered in a sweet and savoury gingery glaze and topped with crunchy cashews and pickled radishes for the perfect balance of flavour and texture.
